com.jereibaselibrary.db.litepal

类 LitePalBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jereibaselibrary.db.litepal.LitePalBase
  • 直接已知子类:
    Generator, Many2ManyAnalyzer, One2OneAnalyzer

    public abstract class LitePalBase
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class of all the LitePal components. If each component need to interactive with other components or they have some same logic with duplicate codes, LitePalBase may be the solution.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.1

      • getTableModel

        protected TableModel getTableModel(java.lang.String className)
        This method is used to get the table model by the class name passed in. The principle to generate table model is that each field in the class with non-static modifier and has a type among int/Integer, long/Long, short/Short, float/Float, double/Double, char/Character, boolean/Boolean or String, would generate a column with same name as corresponding field. If users don't want some of the fields map a column, declare an ignore annotation with Column.ignore().
        参数:
        className - The full name of the class to map in database.
        返回:
        A table model with table name, class name and the map of column name and column type.

      • getSupportedFields

        protected java.util.List<java.lang.reflect.Field> getSupportedFields(java.lang.String className)
        Find all the fields in the class. But not each field is supported to add a column to the table. Only the basic data types and String are supported. This method will intercept all the types which are not supported and return a new list of supported fields.
        参数:
        className - The full name of the class.
        返回:
        A list of supported fields.

      • getSupportedGenericFields

        protected java.util.List<java.lang.reflect.Field> getSupportedGenericFields(java.lang.String className)
        Find all supported generic fields in the class. Supporting rule is in BaseUtility.isGenericTypeSupported(String).
        参数:
        className - The full name of the class.
        返回:
        A list of supported generic fields.

      • isIdColumn

        protected boolean isIdColumn(java.lang.String columnName)
        Judge the passed in column is an id column or not. The column named id or _id will be considered as id column.
        参数:
        columnName - The name of column.
        返回:
        Return true if it's id column, otherwise return false.

      • getForeignKeyColumnName

        protected java.lang.String getForeignKeyColumnName(java.lang.String associatedTableName)
        If two tables are associated, one table have a foreign key column. The foreign key column name will be the associated table name with _id appended.
        参数:
        associatedTableName - The associated table name.
        返回:
        The foreign key column name.
